 n=\"III\" id=\"n79791.11\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">before, above</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">π. τοὐμοῦ πόθου προὔθεντο τὴν τυραννίδα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg007.perseus-grc1:418\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OC\">OC</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">418</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n79791.12\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">instead of</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀδελφῶν πάρος . . θανεῖν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg004.perseus-grc1:536\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Heracl.\">Heracl.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">536</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> —When <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πάρος</foreign> is a Prep. it usually follows its case, but not always, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg007.perseus-grc1:418\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OC\">OC</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">418</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg006.perseus-grc1:1112\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Andr.\">Andr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1112</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg006.perseus-grc1:1208\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1208</biblScope></bibl>. (Cf. Skt. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TE